data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom home nestled on a sprawling 2-acre lot, offering an abundance of privacy and natural beauty. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the stunning hardwood floors that flow throughout most of the home. The heart of this home is the spacious eat-in kitchen, featuring exquisite granite countertops, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space for all your culinary needs.  Step outside into your expansive backyard with two sheds, a trex porch, and a private side patio. The master bedroom is a retreat in itself, featuring a full bath with double sinks, a skylight, and a private balcony/deck overlooking the backyard. Additional features include a U-shaped driveway for ample parking and easy access, ensuring convenience and comfort for you and your guests. Don't miss your opportunity to own this remarkable property. Schedule a showing today and make this dream home yours!
